infores:intact.name: IntAct Molecular Interaction Database
infores:intact.description: The IntAct Molecular Interaction Database provides open access to molecular interactions data derived from literature curation or direct user submission.
infores:intact.fullCitation: N. Del Toro et al., “The IntAct database: efficient access to fine-grained molecular interaction data,” Nucleic Acids Res., vol. 50, no. D1, pp. D648–D653, Jan. 2022, PMID: 34761267
